Install 
go get github.com/smartystreets/goconvey
npm install -g newman
 
Goconvery 
Runs tests when you save a file. 
Start goconvery 
can be started on different port and host as below
goconvey -port=9000 -host=0.0.0.0
hit the url and you should be able to see what is happening. 
 
Newman 
Tests api end points in PSN . 
newman -c PSN.json.postman_collection -e Test.postman_environment
 
PSN.json.postman_collection - tells what test to run 
Test.postman_environment - what host to run the tests against. 

 
Just regular go tests can be run but going into the directory 
go test - will run all the tests in the dir.
 To run a specific test 
go test xxxx_test.go xxxx.go
